interpretation:
The "person rowing boat" card is all about taking control of your own destiny and making your own way in the world. This card suggests that you are in charge of your own journey and that you have the power to steer yourself in the direction you want to go. Whether you are facing choppy waters or calm seas, this card reminds you that you have the strength and determination to navigate any obstacle that comes your way. 

Associated keywords for this card include independence, self-reliance, perseverance, and determination. This card also suggests that you may need to put in some hard work and effort to achieve your goals, but that the rewards will be worth it in the end. Ultimately, the "person rowing boat" card encourages you to trust in yourself and your abilities, and to take the helm of your own life with confidence and courage.
